    {
      "section_id": "para_53",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "An  Act  relating  to  penal  servitude,  methods  of  imprisonment  and \nwhipping; and for purposes connected therewith.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_54",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "[Peninsular Malaysia—30 April 1953; \nSabah and Sarawak—8 November 1991, P.U. (A) 407/1991; \nFederal Territory of Labuan—8 November 1991,  \nP.U. (A) 408/1991]",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_55",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "Short title and application",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_56",
      "heading": "1.  (1) This Act may be cited as the Criminal Justice Act 1953.",
      "content": "1.  (1) This Act may be cited as the Criminal Justice Act 1953.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_57",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(2)  This Act shall *apply to the Peninsular Malaysia only.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_58",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "Abolition of penal servitude, rigorous and simple imprisonment",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_59",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "2. (1) No person shall be sentenced by a court to penal servitude; and \nevery  law  conferring  power  on  a  court  to  pass  a  sentence  of  penal \nservitude in any case shall be construed as conferring power to pass a \nsentence  of  imprisonment  for  a  term  not  exceeding  the  maximum \nterm of penal servitude for which a sentence could have been passed \nin that case immediately before the commencement of *this Act.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_60",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "*NOTE—For  application \n8 November 1991 and  P.U. (A) 408/1991 w.e.f 8 November 1991.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_61",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "in  Sabah,  Sarawak  and  Labuan—see  P.U.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_62",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(A)  407/1991  w.e.f",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_63",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "6                                   Laws of Malaysia                              ACT 345",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_64",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(2)  No  person  shall  be  sentenced  by  a  court  to  rigorous \nimprisonment  or  to  simple  imprisonment;  and  every  law  conferring \npower on a court to pass a sentence of rigorous imprisonment, simple \nimprisonment  or  imprisonment  of  either  description,  shall  be \nconstrued as conferring power to pass a sentence of imprisonment for \na  term  not  exceeding  the  term  for  which  a  sentence  of  rigorous \nimprisonment,  simple  imprisonment  or  imprisonment  of  either \ndescription  could  have  been  passed  in  that  case  immediately  before \nthe commencement of *this Act.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_65",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(3)  Any  person  who  immediately  before  the  commencement  of \n*this  Act  was  undergoing  or  liable  to  undergo  a  term  of  penal \nservitude  under  a  sentence  passed  by  any  court  or  as  a  commuted \npunishment for an offence for which he was sentenced to death, shall \nbe  treated  thereafter  as  if  he  had  been  sentenced  to,  or  were \nundergoing  or  liable  to  undergo,  imprisonment  and  not  penal \nservitude for that term.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_66",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(4)  Any  person  who  immediately  before  the  commencement  of \n*this  Act  was  undergoing  or  liable  to  undergo  a  term  of  rigorous \nimprisonment or of simple imprisonment under a sentence passed by \nany court or as a commuted punishment for an offence for which he \nwas sentenced to  death,  shall be treated thereafter as if  he had been \nsentenced to, or were undergoing or liable to undergo, imprisonment \nand not rigorous imprisonment or simple imprisonment for that term.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_67",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "Life sentences",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_68",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "*3.  Where  any  person  is  treated  as  having  been  sentenced  or  is \nhereafter  sentenced  to  imprisonment  for  life,  such  sentence  shall  be \ndeemed for all purposes  to  be a sentence of imprisonment  for thirty \nyears.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_69",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "*NOTE—For  application \n8 November 1991 and  P.U. (A) 408/1991 w.e.f 8 November 1991.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
