    {
      "section_id": "para_74",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "4.    No  person  shall  be  sentenced  by  a  court  to  whipping  with  a  \ncat-o’-nine tails; and every law conferring power on a court to pass a \nsentence  of  whipping  with  a  cat-o’-nine  tails,  or  whipping,  shall  be \nconstrued as conferring power to pass a sentence of whipping with a \nrattan.",
